    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so heavy. like i'm dragging this massive weight of existence around for no reason. everyone keeps telling me \"it gets better\" or \"there's purpose,\" but they're just lying to feel better about themselves. if there's really nothing out there, then why do we have to keep pretending that we have to stay in this loop?",
